This application uses a component-based architecture with **Tailwind CSS**. This means there isn't one single "CSS file" that controls everything. Instead, the "look" is distributed across two layers:

### 1. The Global Theme & Fonts (`index.html`)
This is the master file that sets the **font** (Inter), the **main background color** (`#050510`), and the **glass-morphism effects** used across every page.

**File:** `index.html`
```html
<head>
    <!-- 1. TAILWIND CSS (The Design System) -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>

    <!-- 2. FONTS (Inter from Google Fonts) -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- 3. GLOBAL CUSTOM STYLES -->
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; /* Sets the font for the whole app */
            background-color: #050510;        /* Sets the dark background color */
            color: #ffffff;                   /* Sets default text to white */
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        }

        /* The "Glass" look used on cards */
        .glass-panel {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        /* The Purple-to-Blue gradient text */
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a855f7 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
    </style>
</head>
```

### 2. Specific Page Layouts & Colors
The specific layout, buttons, and colors for each page are defined inside that page's specific file using Tailwind classes (e.g., `text-purple-500`, `bg-white/5`).

*   **Landing Page:** `pages/Landing.tsx` (Determines the hero section, the orbs in the background, the "Get Started" buttons).
*   **Dashboard:** `pages/Dashboard.tsx` (Determines the layout of the stats, the welcome card, and the progress bars).
*   **Marketplace:** `pages/Marketplace.tsx` (Determines the grid of funding cards and the search bar).
*   **Profile:** `pages/ProfileForm.tsx` (Determines the input forms and document upload areas).
*   **Login/Signup:** `pages/Auth.tsx` (Determines the login box styling).

If you want to change the **overall vibe** (like switching from Dark Mode to Light Mode, or changing the Font), you edit **`index.html`**. If you want to change how a **specific button or card looks**, you edit the file in **`pages/`**.

